r.\n\"Pr\u00e1cticamente no hay contraindicaciones para la ortiga, pero tal vez hay que tener m\u00e1s cuidado con las enfermedades estomacales como la gastritis o la \u00falcera\", advirti\u00f3 el m\u00e9dico.", "language": null, "image": "https://cdn2.img.sputniknews.lat/images/sharing/article/spa/1091972649.jpg?1593861607", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["https://sputniknews.lat", "https://sputniknews.lat", "https://sputniknews.lat/20200704/", "https://sputniknews.lat/20200704/la-mala-hierba-que-puede-reforzar-tu-sistema-inmunologico-1091972649.html", "/", "#", "https://sputniknews.lat/20200704/la-mala-hierba-que-puede-reforzar-tu-sistema-inmunologico-1091972649.html", "https://sputniknews.lat", "https://www.telegram.me/sputnikmundo", "https://t.me/SputnikMundoVideo", "https://twitter.com/SputnikMundo", "https://vk.com/sputnikmundo", "https://odysee.com/@SputnikMundo:1", "https://rutube.ru/channel/24153709/", "https://www.tiktok.com/@sputnik.mundo", "https://www.threads.net/@sputnikmundo", "https://sputniknews.lat/i/logo/logo.png", "https://sputniknews.lat/i/logo/logo.png", "https://sputniknews.lat", "https://www.telegram.me/sputnikmundo", "https://t.me/SputnikMundoVideo", "https://twitter.com/SputnikMundo", "https://vk.com/sputnikmundo", "https://odysee.com/@SputnikMundo:1", "https://rutube.ru/channel/24153709/", "https://www.tiktok.com/@sputnik.mundo", "https://www.threads.net/@sputnikmundo", "https://sputniknews.lat/i/logo/logo.png", "https://sputniknews.lat/i/logo/logo.png", "https://sputniknews.lat", "https://www.telegram.me/sputnikmundo", "https://t.me/SputnikMundoVideo", "https://twitter.com/SputnikMundo", "https://vk.com/sputnikmundo", "https://odysee.com/@SputnikMundo:1", "https://rutube.ru/channel/24153709/", "https://www.tiktok.com/@sputnik.mundo", "https://www.threads.net/@sputnikmundo", "https://sputniknews.lat/i/logo/logo.png", "https://sputniknews.lat/i/logo/logo.png", "https://cdn1.img.sputniknews.lat/img/109197/26/1091972607_0:134:1920:1220_19